## Code Organization

### Module / Feature Structure
```
<feature-name>/
├── <entry point>         # Public API of this module
├── <implementation>      # Internal logic
├── <types/interfaces>    # Type definitions
└── <tests>               # Co-located or in __tests__/
```

### Import Order
```<language>
# 1. Standard library
# 2. Third-party / external
# 3. Internal / local (absolute paths)
# 4. Relative imports (avoid where possible)
```

### File Length
- <e.g., Prefer files under 300 lines. Split by responsibility, not by line count.>
- <e.g., A file that imports from itself is a sign it needs to be split.>

